        <span class="text-gradient">Education Management.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        A unified platform automating every department: <strong>Admissions, Academics, Finance, Transport, Boarding, and E-Learning</strong>. Stop using isolated spreadsheets.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="#administration" class="bg-orange-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-orange-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-orange-600/30">
          View Full Feature List
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          Download Brochure
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Fee Collection</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">100% Automated</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Grading</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">CBC, 8-4-4, IGCSE</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Portals</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Student & Parent</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-bold text-slate-900">Timetable</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Auto-Generation</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="sticky top-[72px] z-40 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-y border-slate-200 py-4 hidden md:block">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">
      <a href="#administration" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Administration</a>
      <a href="#finance" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Finance & Fees</a>
      <a href="#academics" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Academics</a>
      <a href="#operations" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Operations</a>
      <a href="#portals" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Portals & Apps</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section id="administration" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white border-b border-slate-100">
