              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Capture Medical History, Allergies, and Special Needs.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Manage Sibling links for family billing.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Generate Student ID Cards with Barcodes.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">HR & Staff Management</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Staff Database (TSC / Board Employed).</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Leave Management & Approval Workflow.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Teacher Load Allocation & Performance tracking.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Payroll Processing (P9, Payslips, Bank Files).</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Disciplinary Module</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Record cases, punishments, and suspensions.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Automated notification letters to parents.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Track behavioral trends per student.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Alumni Management</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span>‚Ä¢</span> Database of past students and contacts.</li>
