        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-10">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-4">Fee Management</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Fee Structures:</strong> Define fees per class, boarding status, or new admission.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Invoicing:</strong> Bulk invoice entire classes at term start.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Waivers/Bursaries:</strong> Manage scholarships and CDF allocations.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Arrears Management:</strong> Auto-block access to exams/portal for defaulters.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-4">School Accounting</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Vote Heads:</strong> Track budget vs actuals per vote head (e.g., Tuition, Transport).</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Petty Cash:</strong> Requisition and approval workflow.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Suppliers:</strong> LPO generation and supplier aging reports.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><strong>Reports:</strong> Balance Sheet, Trial Balance, Income Statement.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="academics" class="py-24 px-6 bg-orange-50/50 border-b border-orange-100">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Academics & E-Learning</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">Comprehensive tools for 8-4-4, IGCSE, and the Competency Based Curriculum (CBC).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
