          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">Define grading scales, exam weights (CATs/Main), and subject clusters. Auto-calculate mean scores, streams positions, and value added progress.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Graphical Performance Trends</li>
